    dc:description "Fig. 2. Head sculpture and femora shapes. A, C, Aenictus guineensis (CASENT0876634). B, Aenictus xegi sp. nov. (NHMUK012849243). D, Aenictus susanae sp. nov. (CASENT0406729)." ;
